{
  "title": "misalisinay caay kapahezek ku pinanam tu lalangawan",
  "titleCh": "祭禮人終身學習的文化意義",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "碎裂後的撒奇萊雅族祭禮文化、制度與組織，雖然歷經數代族人努力縫合與重製，仍是千瘡百孔的模樣，難以完整復原。幸而「傳統」與「文化」本身便具有滾動前進的特性，不論巨變或微動，都將以適應當代社會與環境為前提而持續演化，撒奇萊雅族祭禮文化的實踐，仍可能在自主意識下穩定發展其特色。",
      "ab": "zikuz nu kaluminak nu Sakizaya a lalangawan nu lisin, hecek atu kasabulud, anu pinapina tu a kasalaylay nu binacadan paicelang mikudepu atu miliyaw misanga’, malecad u maluminakay azihen, caay kadayum mitiku tu sumamaday. nika u “laylay” atu “lalangawan” izaw ku taayaway a culil, anu masumad atu maisiz, taneng misuayaw tu syakay atu liwliw malalid a masumad, pileku nu Sakizaya a binacadan tu lisin nu lalangawan, taneng micuwat tu nabalucu’an a mikawaw.",
